The paper discusses the development and research in the domain of autonomous vehicles, specifically self-driving miniature cars. This falls under the category of Robotics (cs.RO) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the design and realization of a standardized platform for research and experiments, which falls under the category of Systems and Control (cs.SY) and Software Engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper discusses the use of simulation-based development and validation, which falls under the category of Machine Learning (cs.LG).
